Text:
Hard to believe nobody's commented on the quality yet.  Video is decent (I'd say 7 or 8 out of 10); audio is horribly compressed, possibly even up-sampled from a lower-quality source; very tinny.  Also, the video is full-frame rather than widescreen.

All that said, I do want to still say thanks, maximersk.  May not be as great as I'd hoped for, but it's better than nothing.
